## Project Structure
- `LibraryManagementSystem.java`: Main class containing the `main` method.
- `Book.java`: Class representing a book with title, author, ISBN, and availability.
- `Library.java`: Class managing the collection of books and implementing library operations.
- `User.java`: Class representing a library user with a unique identifier and borrowed books.
- *Any additional classes for specific book types.*

## Extension
Feel free to explore and extend the functionality of the project. You can add more features, improve the user interface, or implement additional book types.

